                        <interp inst="t18440610-name-169" type="given" value="EVERARD"></interp>EVERARD PARKINS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I heard a cry of "Stop thief!"—I found this soap in an area—I took Hearley to the station-house.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
